title: #130: Whatever Doesn't Kill You (@WhitneyCummings, @BillyWayneDavis)
itunes:title: Whatever Doesn't Kill You with Whitney Cummings, Billy Wayne Davis
description: Whitney Cummings had me over to the place she was staying in while in New York and we talked about her hardships at The Comedy Store, with her sitcom, and as a child of an alcoholic. I had no idea she felt that way about when she was starting at the Store. She always seemed so on top of it all the time, I couldn't even imagine it being difficult for her. Billy Wayne Davis joins me for the intro.
